HEADWORD: Direct-coupled
<hw>Di*rect"-cou"pled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Coupled
without intermediate connections, as an engine and a dynamo.</def></p>

<p><cs><col><b>Direct-coupled antenna</b></col> <fld>(Wireless
Teleg.)</fld>, <cd>an antenna connected electrically with one point of a
closed oscillation circuit in syntony with it and earthed.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

